HEADWORD: Gherkin
<hw>Gher"kin</hw> <pr>(g⟦etil⟧r"k⟦icr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.
<ets>agurkje</ets>, a dim. akin to G. <ets>gurke</ets>, Dan.
